data.description: Fantastic Roosevelt Park Ranch!  This 3 bedroom full basement ranch, is neat, clean, has had great care over the years and is ready to go!  Newer furnace, 8 year old roof shingles and is vinyl sided too!  Beautiful plaster walls, finished recreation room with bar, huge laundry and utility area as well including an extra shower area and separate toilet in basement ''shelter''.  Super location just one house away from the nearest of many playgrounds in the area.  Oversized 1 1/2 car garage and a great backyard.  Located on charming Cornell Road and not to last long!
